snippet.textDisplay: I think Indian composers can do better when it comes to performing on big stage like this . We are no short of stories . We have glorious stories of heroes like Shree ram , Bajrangbali Hanumanji, Lord Karn, goddess Durga Maa ,Goddess Kali Maa which can be beautifully told through these platforms . I can envision some great revolutionary music if you as a team can implement what I have kept before you . The song could be a fusion of both modern and old school tunes , the fusion of an intense and a sober style of music which fits very well with the personalities of our Gods and Godesses. Give it a try . Best of luck
